cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.HC. 

The paper deals with a problem in Visual Dialogue, which involves natural language processing, computer vision, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a Bayesian model, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on two goal-oriented dialogue datasets, which involves human-computer interaction, and thus falls under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
